{"tid":112624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"ust南亞仔成日話融入香港，又叫大家唔好用蝻呢個字眼","createTime":"2017-02-08T09:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T18:11:36.000Z","uid":90,"like":37,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb1f527b366fa1aa242418a238d14ee637e735f1","tid":112624,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁融入香港<br />\n我諗啫係當自己係香港嘅一份子喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/08/171558_13b411590893d0e9b8f2162549fbaa21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F171558_13b411590893d0e9b8f2162549fbaa21.jpg&h=37edefe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咩意思先？<br />\n笑鳩香港人？<br />\n真係香港人會笑得出？<br />\n<br />\n之後佢又叫大家唔好用蝻呢啲字眼<br />\n話標籤啊又剩，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/451uN19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F451uN19.jpg&h=ded00e45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己又用on9台仔去標籤台灣人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩意思先？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有個好似蓋清講嘅<br />\n有啲南亞細路，香港出世<br />\n但都唔識中文<br />\n真係想融入香港？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識自己語言唔識廣東話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係香港人唔比機會佢地？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有睇下香港電影個啲點都學到一兩句喇，其他國家人都得喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係冇心學定冇機會啊？"},{"pid":"875663a9a38ed4371a77f439139e6548d0e439d0","tid":112624,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:57:24.000Z","msg":"我諗啲細路應該識講屌你老母嘅"},{"pid":"2708cea533a35ec57b859028dd43097a3e3e9581","tid":112624,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,